In src/core/analyzers/unused.rs, DependencyType is used with fallback_type passed by value multiple times in parse_dependency_array, but it does not implement Copy.

```rust
fn parse_dependency_array(items: &[Value], fallback_type: DependencyType) -> Result<Vec<UnusedDep>> {
    for item in items {
        // ...
        dependency_type: fallback_type,  // moved each iteration - will fail on second item
    }
}
```

Impact: Code will fail to compile when parsing multiple dependencies of the same type in an array. The first iteration moves fallback_type, subsequent iterations fail.

Fix: Add Copy and Clone derives to DependencyType in src/core/output.rs:
```rust
